---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - OptyP" description="Terms and Conditions for OptyP professional resume and profile optimization services.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        By using OptyP services, you agree to comply with the following terms and conditions. 
        Please read these terms carefully before engaging our services.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Service Agreement</h2>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            By engaging OptyP's services, you enter into a binding agreement to receive professional resume 
            and profile optimization services as described in your selected plan.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>Services include but are not limited to: ATS-compliant resume creation, LinkedIn profile optimization, and portfolio website development</li>
            <li>Service delivery timeframes are outlined in your specific service package</li>
            <li>All services are delivered digitally unless otherwise specified</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <p class="font-medium">You agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Provide accurate information:</strong> Supply truthful, complete, and up-to-date information about your career history, skills, and achievements</li>
            <li><strong>Timely communication:</strong> Respond to our requests for information within reasonable timeframes</li>
            <li><strong>Cooperation:</strong> Work collaboratively with our team to ensure quality optimization of your profiles</li>
            <li><strong>Content approval:</strong> Review and approve deliverables within the specified review period</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Use our services in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Payment Terms</h2>
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Payment schedule:</strong> Payment must be completed before service delivery begins</li>
            <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> All prices are listed in Indian Rupees (₹) and are subject to change without prior notice</li>
            <li><strong>Payment methods:</strong> We accept major credit cards, debit cards, and digital payment methods</li>
            <li><strong>No refunds:</strong> Unless specified in our refund policy, payments are non-refundable once services begin</li>
            <li><strong>Late payments:</strong> Services may be suspended for accounts with overdue payments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
            <p class="font-medium text-yellow-800 mb-2">✓ Your Content Ownership</p>
            <p>All deliverables provided by OptyP (including optimized resumes, LinkedIn profiles, and websites) become your property after full payment completion.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>You retain all rights to your personal information and career content</li>
            <li>OptyP retains rights to our methodologies, templates, and proprietary processes</li>
            <li>You may use our deliverables for personal career advancement without restriction</li>
            <li>You may not resell, redistribute, or claim authorship of our proprietary methods</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Service Guarantees & Limitations</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-green-800 mb-2">✓ What We Guarantee</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>• ATS-compliant resume formatting</li>
                <li>• Professional content optimization</li>
                <li>• Timely delivery as per agreed schedule</li>
                <li>• Two rounds of revisions included</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
              <h4 class="font-medium text-red-800 mb-2">✗ What We Cannot Guarantee</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>• Job interview or employment outcomes</li>
                <li>• Specific response rates from employers</li>
                <li>• Results from factors beyond our control</li>
                <li>• Compatibility with all ATS systems</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            OptyP's liability is limited to the amount paid for services. We are not liable for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of our services</li>
            <li>Lost profits, lost business opportunities, or career outcomes</li>
            <li>Damages resulting from third-party actions or decisions</li>
            <li>Technical issues beyond our reasonable control</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Confidentiality</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            We maintain strict confidentiality of your personal and professional information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Your information is used solely for service delivery</li>
            <li>We do not share client information with third parties without consent</li>
            <li>All team members sign confidentiality agreements</li>
            <li>Data is securely stored and transmitted</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">Either party may terminate services under the following conditions:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Completion of agreed-upon services</li>
            <li>Mutual agreement to terminate</li>
            <li>Breach of terms by either party</li>
            <li>Non-payment or non-cooperation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p>
            These terms are governed by the laws of India. Any disputes will be resolved through 
            binding arbitration in accordance with Indian arbitration laws.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions About Our Terms?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
          For terms-related inquiries or clarifications, please contact our support team.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Contact Form:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">Visit our contact page</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>